  "claim": {
    "id": "CLM-42",
    "text": "Lovs & Co. s.r.o. (IČO 10847031, founded 14 May 2021) was co-owned 50/50 by Vít Schlesinger and Lukáš Oslzla, both jednatelé. On 13 February 2024 the company was renamed Artstay s.r.o., Schlesinger's jednatel role and 50 % ended, and Oslzla became sole (100 %) owner — ten days before Oslzla's exit from Blackfish completed on 23 February 2024.",
    "status": "VERIFIED_PRIMARY",
    "note": "CORRECTION: the earlier record had the renaming direction reversed (it said Artstay was 'later renamed Lovs & Co.').",
    "sources": [
      "SRC-12"
    ]
  },
